    "description": "Guidance for issuing warranty parts ahead of purchased parts to avoid failure-to-return chargebacks.",
    "usedWhen": "A case includes both warranty and purchased parts, warranty parts are available first, and delaying warranty repair would risk failure-to-return chargebacks."
